sequenceDiagram
    
    actor g as Guest
    actor r as Resident
    participant i as Sensor
    participant c as Controller
    participant a as Actuator
    participant s as Server

    note over g,s : Case 1 (Resident from OUTSIDE)
    r->>i: Enter code
    i->>c: Send code
    c->>c: Authenticate code
    alt ALLOWED
    c->>a: Open door
    else NOT ALLOWED
    c->>a: Deny Access
    end

    note over g,s : Case 2 (GUEST from OUTSIDE)
    g->>r: Request access
    r->>s: Request OPT
    s->>r: Generate OPT
    s-->>c: OTP
    r->>g: Share OTP
    g->>i: Enter code
    i->>c: Send code
    c->>c: Authenticate code
    alt ALLOWED
    c->>a: Open door
    else NOT ALLOWED
    c->>a: Deny Access
    end

    note over g,s : Case 3 (from INSIDE)
    r->i: Sense person
    i->>c: Notify
    c->>a: Open door

    note over g,s : Case 4 (EMERGENCY)
    loop Data sampling
    i->>s: Enviroment data
    s->>s: Process data
    end
    s->>s: Detect emergency
    s-->>c: Alert emergency
    c->>a: Open door
